{"tid":308556,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢間公司相當有嫌疑","createTime":"2017-07-04T09:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T09:37:50.000Z","uid":82018,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"baa215dcb31cbec54bcf4e6ede413753024a692e","tid":308556,"uid":82018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T09:14:26.000Z","msg":"之前上網搵炒散做<br />\n見到有間公司請人打電話90-150$一個鐘 <br />\n即刻申請左 去到發現其實係做cold call<br />\n個office好細 200-300呎到 無咩裝修 好似可以隨時走人咁<br />\n間公司最近幫緊信貸公司做宣傳<br />\n所以每日要做嘅就係睇電話list逐個打去讀稿<br />\n本身都無咩野 但最近同一齊返工嘅女仔都發現左d奇怪嘅現象<br />\n<br />\n1）間公司每一日都請緊新人<br />\n2）so far已知做過最長嘅人都只係4星期，無人出過糧<br />\n3）佢張list唔單只有電話，仲有個個人嘅身份證號碼、住咩類型號樓、月收入、每月供款<br />\n4）人工咁高<br />\n5） google唔到佢公司名，大廈gf嘅牌個個單位顯示嘅都唔係佢公司名<br />\n<br />\n佢話下星期出糧，不過我地個個都擔心佢會走數，諗住做埋呢個月就走人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd92e9a7fbe77d293a37c5542ee549f83721204","tid":308556,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T09:29:50.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日換人<br />\n有個最長先4星期<br />\n你仲想做成個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455f6f46c10f173381b86177e6bfb319f989c3e5","tid":308556,"uid":82018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T09:31:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日換人<br />\n有個最長先4星期<br />\n你仲想做成個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我指等佢出埋糧走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7d48f43b2155095f8ca5e0e0486a465f2528bf","tid":308556,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T09:37:50.000Z","msg":"有無合約？無你就準備走都得啦"}]}